Package splEvolutionCore.candidateSelector

Class PositiveVariationPointCandidateTemplates

java.lang.Object
splEvolutionCore.candidateSelector.VariationPointCandidate
splEvolutionCore.candidateSelector.PositiveVariationPointCandidateTemplates
public class PositiveVariationPointCandidateTemplates extends VariationPointCandidate
Parameterized form of callable code constructs for given positive variation point -instantiated callable constructs are assigned later -stores also basic information about variation point
Author:
Jakub Perdek
